title: STUNNING CORNER UNIT IN PARAMOUNT BAY!!
posting_body: ['Stunning corner unit with floor-to-ceiling windows at the elegant Paramount Bay.', 'Enjoy unobstructed direct bay views of Biscayne Bay & Miami Beach from this oversized turnkey 2 Bedroom / 2.5 bathroom.', 'This residence comes fully furnished w/ Artefacto & RH furnishings & Purple brand mattresses.', 'The unit has been fully upgraded & features a private elevator entry, 10’ ceilings, a gorgeous 8’ deep terrace & Kohler Master Steam Shower with DTV-2 custom showering experience.', 'The kitchen includes SUBZERO & WOLF appliances, a wine cooler, and an open island.', 'Porcelanosa tiled floors, recessed LED lighting, glass-sliding “barn” doors in master suite & much more.', 'The Paramount Bay is a full service building, offers 2 pools (East & West facing) along w/ cabanas, a state-of-the-art gym & much more.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
